{"tid":1660120,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"工程撚教你，硬碟變防彈護心鏡","createTime":"2019-10-17T10:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T19:44:50.000Z","uid":89641,"like":59,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b6525097bf6cd8f63847bbe81f80f857a34826d0","tid":1660120,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"我呢就好怕死既，而家啲狗會開槍打人，自然會更加驚，佢地又咁中意打心口，所以我地要整返塊護心鏡會好啲。<br />\n<br />\n咁大家都會成日運動，材料自然要輕，但膠板係不切實際的，因為子陣講既係穿刺同撞擊力。<br />\n香港「買」避陣衣又犯法喎，咁就要諗辦法自製啦！<br />\n唔知大家有無拆過HARDDISK呢？<br />\n咩容量都得架，因為「硬碟」唔係浪得虛名，入面隻碟真係鋁合金仲要加硬過，經過我不標準既測試，一塊片厚1.5mm左右，我用鎚仔+縲絲成個人跳起 大力打落去，粒左但唔穿。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗用到2.5毫米鋁板咁大件事，佢係合金，見硬磨光切裁都做好曬，就等你將佢由廢料中拯救出來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrzWnar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrzWnar.jpg&h=742c27f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7R5ZW9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7R5ZW9.jpg&h=959c6055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一般來講，一隻硬碟有4塊，用雙面膠紙痴係衫入面，或者直接用AA膠，就可以得到臨時避彈衣。<br />\n驚死既拆多幾個，整金鏤玉衣都得，唔會好重！<br />\n聽日搵啲硬度測試比數據你地睇下。"},{"pid":"8adcde768c1a3d33486537041cb5c3bc2f782d7b","tid":1660120,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f4eb1141017bbe205235689bed4643c6d3472d67","tid":1660120,"uid":301936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"f50a0fb3aa37b2958c34d598080a6f252446bad6","tid":1660120,"uid":66325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:29:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr