:32:50.000Z","msg":"我就係見佢狂開，我哋要更加合法保護自己。"},{"pid":"2ea6eada6107a7c392c6e53a0dbfce8e59e18a2d","tid":1660120,"uid":89641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25476cc9fb77610a93b52e580def81591b9166c6","tid":1660120,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:32:19.000Z","msg":"Hitachi 玻璃碟得唔得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:34:21.000Z","msg":"係喎，有期興玩玻璃碟，唔得呀，會脆到散開，執返啲垃圾segate toshiba西電算啦"},{"pid":"2dff2bc1bf6abc97b1f892ffd17bb42e8ba4e451","tid":1660120,"uid":21920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"係咪真係防到<br />\n你個test準唔準"},{"pid":"a83328569c4342bacbadb713481da9ddd68fa2b6","tid":1660120,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dff2bc1bf6abc97b1f892ffd17bb42e8ba4e451","tid":1660120,"uid":21920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"係咪真係防到<br />\n你個test準唔準"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"不如自己縫衫 插金屬/陶瓷板好過<br />\n<br />\n得嘅插滿2.5&ldquo;咪唔好？"},{"pid":"e827257d602cef202e6f3ffbf0c581fca9343e5d","tid":1660120,"uid":63119,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"隻碟咁薄，即使子彈穿唔到，衝擊力亦會直接傷到身體。就好似我一拳打落你度，我無打穿你件衫，但你一樣會瘀晒。"},{"pid":"759c2f21b5daf1d6ef737b9667e0869874f23e11","tid":1660120,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e827257d602cef202e6f3ffbf0c581fca9343e5d","tid":1660120,"uid":63119,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"隻碟咁薄，即使子彈穿唔到，衝擊力亦會直接傷到身體。就好似我一拳打落你度，我無打穿你件衫，但你一樣會瘀晒。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:48:13.000Z","msg":"穿內臟傷好多"},{"pid":"ba6a9461a8110736c20c4da9e45bda8352ffeaf2","tid":1660120,"uid":73054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e827257d602cef202e6f3ffbf0c581fca9343e5d","tid":1660120,"uid":63119,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T