Z","msg":"提提你 有啲碟係Glass substrate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇清楚先好試"},{"pid":"2ae8abcfd43c2ca665e9128b3558fb0e0b229132","tid":1660120,"uid":89641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4016c8fc1d3c7fc1a87493b924e1267407cfbce8","tid":1660120,"uid":3678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:24:57.000Z","msg":"提提你 有啲碟係Glass substrate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇清楚先好試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"所以話舊HARDDISK, 我拆果隻係2006年既垃圾SEGATE 150GB....仲要bad sector但仲插係部舊電腦入面...<br />\n其實黃金新高登果D好多2手harddisk, 癲起上來10蚊隻都有, 10蚊可以救你4個心口, 屌你正呀喂, 我係咁諗的。"},{"pid":"660dad590b46b1d0cc601ee46e1d5ba59edafe24","tid":1660120,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4016c8fc1d3c7fc1a87493b924e1267407cfbce8","tid":1660120,"uid":3678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:24:57.000Z","msg":"提提你 有啲碟係Glass substrate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇清楚先好試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:32:52.000Z","msg":"BTW, 玻璃片HHD係2018年後既野,一般勁貴仲要過10TB 我估無人會拆個咁新既HHD掛....<br />\n拆開見到咁樣都仲用既話....我真係唔知點講好 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.itw01.com/images/2018/04/21/08/2337_MQ0EJp_VPWLGEX.jpeg!r800x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.itw01.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F08%2F2337_MQ0EJp_VPWLGEX.jpeg%21r800x0.jpg&h=bb8262fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10671e1ae16238358529e1d32a3f9f958572c4cf","tid":1660120,"uid":265742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T18:31:08.000Z","msg":"正，屋企有好多"},{"pid":"a27b29e3308de544e265ca34d780d60a0836ceb2","tid":1660120,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10671e1ae16238358529e1d32a3f9f958572c4cf","tid":1660120,"uid":265742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T18:31:08.000Z","msg":"正，屋企有好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"今日LAB好多人用, 應該無機會撞了...<br />\n不過我搜集左好多防彈既資料, <br />\n<br />\n以入手難易度排:<br />\n(1) 硬碟片<br />\n現成拆出來就係, 舊HHD極平, 學生仔飲少杯珍奶都買到2個=8片....<br />\n<br />\n(2) 鋁板(3MM 以上)<br />\n&gt; 標準2.5話夠檔0.38, 不過香港板材多數大陸野, 你知的....買厚D<br />\n記得飛邊, 好利的<br />\n<br />\n(3) 碳纖維(可在汽車貼膜入手, 不過一層唔夠, 要貼3層以上)<br />\n其實應該係用PE+碳纖=狗用既韓仔裝<br />\n<br />\n(4) UHMWPE (AMAZON)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1658039/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1658039/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n------<br />\n以安全度排:<br />\n(4) &gt; (1) = (2) &gt; (3) (*因為唔知你貼成點)<br />\n<br />\n以輕便度:<br />\n(3)  &gt;&gt;(1) &gt;(3) &gt;&gt;&gt;(2)"},{"pid":"e9ddcbc0eb3da41c6e681feda6228bb43fffe35d","tid":1660120,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"我有預感如果我呢d地獄黑仔王用 粒子彈係會射中中間個窿"},{"pid":"3b7f426ed3b7f708dbf9b0f68f30e775e14db892","tid":1660120,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9ddcbc0eb3da41c6e681feda6228bb43fffe35d","tid":1660120,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"我有預感如果我呢d地獄黑仔王用 粒子彈係會射中中間個窿"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"用兩張咪得"},{"pid":"5332282f60cf2471ad75abe65ddefb0f30322078","tid":1660120,"uid":89641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b7f426ed3b7f708dbf9b0f68f30e775e14db892","tid":1660120,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9ddcbc0eb3da41c6e681feda6228bb43fffe35d","tid":1660120,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"我有預感如果我呢d地獄黑仔王用 粒子彈係會射中中間個窿"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"用兩張咪得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvquNSG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmvquNSG.jpg&h=ace65a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoWhWL3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.